{"tid":1068463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球30間最清潔航空公司　國泰由榜首跌至第六","createTime":"2019-03-19T09:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T01:14:48.000Z","uid":41404,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"bb665efe09820c7b10eb8b01f84898c27e5764de","tid":1068463,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:10:30.000Z","msg":"獨立航空服務調查機構Skytrax，周一（18日）公布「2018年全球30間最清潔航空公司」，當中日本全日本航空公司（ANA）排名從第三跳升至第一位。至於<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因管理不善而從全球最佳航空公司排名榜排名節節下跌的國泰航空</span></ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，從對上一次調查的榜首，今次下跌至第六位。英美的航空公司則榜上無名。<br />\n<br />\n專家按洗手間、地氈、座椅、行李架的清潔程度作評估，結果全日空勇奪榜首，緊隨其後的分別為台灣長榮航空公司及南韓韓亞航空公司。<br />\n<br />\n此外，新加坡航空公司、日本航空公司、卡塔爾航空公司、瑞士國際航空、海南航空和漢莎航空等，也躋身前十名。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190319/mobile/bkn-20190319021820168-0319_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190319%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190319021820168-0319_00822_001.html&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMa9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=180a7e76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190319/mobile/bkn-20190319021820168-0319_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"60cd8fe305a63113108c0a5339603abf0a69e729","tid":1068463,"uid":43575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:16:45.000Z","msg":"國泰個廁所好污糟！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051f3ba1cc7ee0ede2396e56a37e2a57d8fa53b0","tid":1068463,"uid":31098,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:33:32.000Z","msg":"因航曾經係榜首？<br />\n雖然因航的確唔算污糟，但唔會係最乾淨啊嘛？尤其同日本比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ch